          multiplier: 1.1
          bias: aligned
          rationale: EMI burden eases; demand improves
        FMCG:
          multiplier: 0.9
          bias: aligned
          rationale: Consumption sentiment improves
        IT:
          multiplier: 0.7
          bias: inverse
          rationale: Potential INR weakness can support exporters; sign depends on
            phrasing
